	<!-- message -->
	<p>At any city, and in PoK, there are potion vendors. Go there. Buy Cloudy Potions (+/- 10pp). Put the potion in a main inventory spot. Make a hotbutton for it.<br />
<br />
These potions, while not stackable, are INSTANT cast invis. Meaning... you can click it While Running!!! <br />
<br />
"You feel yourself start to appear..."<br />
Click. Problem solved.<br />
<br />
Enjoy.</p>
	
	
	
