	<p>Anohter Note on Flash of Light (FoL) the mob will stick to the pet if the pet is higher on the agro list then you are when your out of meele range.  To get that mob to run and not bother pup even at extreem range is to drop a couple dots on that bad boy jack yourself way up on the hate list.  That little mobbie wont even give the sweet puppy the time of day.  Found FoL quite handy from level 28-45ish while I was in EW killing wallies and Uthorks.</p>
	
	
	
