<br />
Mad props to Katla, Vova and all the Science of War shamans for creating it.<br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.scienceofwar.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7122" target="_blank">http://www.scienceofwar.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7122</a> <br />
