</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Neat tip I picked up in a post here yesterday from a post by Caanus Grey: <a href="http://forums.interealms.com/shaman/showthread.php?threadid=16641&amp;highlight=target" target="_blank">http://forums.interealms.com/shaman...ighlight=target</a><br />
<br />
I'll reword it to make it a bit simpler.<br />
<br />
Sometimes you have a raid target pretargeted and don't want to lose it, but then get tells for last-minute buffs.<br />
<br />
With your pretarget targeted, hit TAB to target yourself. Now click on the people needing buffs and buff them. When done, target yourself again (using F1, not TAB) and hit TAB. You now have your pretarget back.</p>
	
	
	
		<div>__________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=529003">Twoflower Tourist</a> - <a href="http://www.unionofpower.org">Union of Power</a><br />
65 Prophet<br />
   ... finally<br />
Rodcet Nife</div>
	
	
